translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東ヘルマンの将軍、タイガーだった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was Tiger, the general of East Herman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや〜、ようやく見つけられたよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, I finally found you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 年取るとこういう場所は辛くなるねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Getting old makes places like this tough."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「アアン？　なんだぁ、あの連中は」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Huh? Who are those guys?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、そういや会ったのは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh, come to think of it, the last time we met was

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンスを仲間にする前だったっけ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: before we made Zans our ally."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、いや、待て……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yeah, no, wait..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの制服は見覚えがある。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I recognize those uniforms.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東ヘルマンの連中か」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They're from East Herman."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はんっ、魔王の子暗殺任務を負った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmph, the special forces assigned to the Demon King's child's assassination mission,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 特殊部隊とかその辺か」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: or something like that."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ご明察。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Exactly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さすが、既に赤軍の将軍をやるだけある」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As expected of someone already a general in the Red Army."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それにしても随分と人数が増えたものだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Still, their numbers have increased quite a bit."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「スシヌ・ザ・ガンジー……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Sushinu the Gandhi... you even made the princess of Zess an ally,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼスのお姫様も仲間にしたか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: haven't you?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うーん、知らない子もちらほらいるが……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm, there are also some unfamiliar faces though..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まあ、魔王の子の協力者なら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, if they're collaborators of the Demon King's child,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敵なのは間違いないねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: then they're definitely enemies."
"...Wait a minute,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「前よりも人数増えてない！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: haven't they increased in number since before!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「前回、あれだけの人数で負けたんだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Last time, we lost even with that many people.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: より人数を増やすのは当然だろう？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's only natural they'd increase their numbers more, right?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふんっ、少ねぇよ、タコ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmph, that's still too few, you fool."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……やるしかなさそうだな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Looks like we have no choice but to fight."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ズドン！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Boom!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 元就が身の丈以上ある刀を、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Motonari slammed his sword, taller than himself,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 地面に叩きつけた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: into the ground.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なあ、大将」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey, Commander,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 元就は東ヘルマンの面々を、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Motonari, glaring sharply at the East Herman troops,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 鋭い眼光で睨みつけたまま、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: kept his fierce gaze fixed on them,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 意識だけをあなたに傾けて聞く。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but focused his attention only on you as he asked.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あいつらぁ、大将の友達か？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Are those guys your friends, Commander?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「クク、あの敵意だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Heh heh, with that hostility,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 友達なわけはあるまいなぁ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there's no way they're your friends, right?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なら、やっていいんだな？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So, it's okay to attack, right?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あいつら全員、やっていいんだな？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I can take them all out, right?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「クヒヒヒ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Kuhihihi...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 駄目だと言っても、もう聞かんがな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if you say no, I won't listen anymore."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パンパンに膨らんだ風船のように、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Like a balloon swollen to bursting,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 元就の敵意は今にも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Motonari's hostility was about

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はち切れそうな程に膨らんでいた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: to explode.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おーおー、やる気満々だねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh my, you're raring to go, huh."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やだやだ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No, no..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 好戦的だねぇ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so aggressive..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でも、それでこそ魔王の子だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But that's exactly what makes you the Demon King's child."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうだねぇ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's right.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 当然知ってるさ、それくらい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Of course I know that much."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「こう見えておじさんも……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You know, despite appearances, even I...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 君達みたいな子供を手にかけることに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: feel a deep pain in my heart when having to fight kids like you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 非常に心を痛めてるんだよ？」
「でも……ごめんねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But... I'm sorry.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おじさんはハゲてないよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And by the way, I'm not bald."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: タイガー将軍が片手を上げる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: General Tiger raised one hand.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「全員、目標に突撃」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Everyone, charge the target!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 東ヘルマンの兵隊が一斉に突撃してきた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The East Herman soldiers charged forward all at once.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひーっ、来た来た来たー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Eek, here they come, here they come!"
